     mono support, improved handling of the 5430, 5434, and transparent
     text acceleration.
 48. Preliminary code for detecting S3 864/964 and AT&T 20C498 (Harald Koenig).
 47. Generic VGA256 driver -- works only at 320x200 (Harm Hanemaayer)
